Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.99,0:00:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看什麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.16,0:00:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇場版 灼眼的夏娜炭

Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 瑪利安奴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼又弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.13,0:00:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都是這樣 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 縫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.07,0:00:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定要小心喔 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗利安格內大人

Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些串燒真是好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.12,0:01:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 能不能不要在我頭上吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.28,0:01:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了吵死了吵死了

Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.19,0:01:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在我頭上的那個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近都沒看見她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是戈壁沙漠 今天的沙塵暴也非常厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.16,0:01:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放大畫面

Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖地往這裡看過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的就是你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴眼鏡的你 看這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別因為我小就無視我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家也叫你火炬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 把眼睛看過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.62,0:01:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在幹什麼啊 奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:02:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為戴上眼鏡就帥了那就大錯特錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了

Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我很喜歡這裡的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 所以就到這裡來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也很喜歡那座山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海會死掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山會死掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 還有很多想要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能就這麼消失掉

Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了你哦 緣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個

Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能僅用一把刀就擋住我得意的寶具「正規升半音號」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 非常的抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係喔 瑪麗安奴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄壞了一個還有很多個呢

Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是稍微鼓起點勇氣了再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼 快點放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋怎麼吃人家的點心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了吵死了吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來這裡幫你吃東西 快感謝我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是給你吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你這樣子可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都聽厭了 煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛 你幹什麼啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點放我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我過來 我要跟你決一勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別總呆在那…

Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼身體滑溜溜的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 比起這種事 噢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2007年秋季 危機將再度出現在那孩子面前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 這裡到底是哪裡啊

Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我游…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我游…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我游…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我游…
